data.title: About Francis Ibarreta
data.text:
Thank You For Viewing My Site. I appreciate it. Even Though This Site Is Still Under Construction, Rest Assured To See More Pictures To Be Posted In The Future.

I'm just a simple guy who dream to be one of the model and a photographer someday. I love taking pictures, web design, photo editing and so on. So I realize that I have an eye to be part of this industry. So I'm challenging myself to achieve it. I enjoy being with my friends, bar hopping and etc. I know I have lots of flaws in me but that doesn't stop me from moving forward and getting ready for the next adventure.

"Nobody can go back and start a new beginning, but anyone can start today and make a new ending. And, Dream as if you'll live forever, live as if you'll die today."
